<div class="text-container">
            <h1>Sticking to the Recipe</h1>

            <p>
                The distinct Windsor style has contributed to the success of local pizzerias. From shredded pepperoni, galati cheese, canned mushrooms, and cornmeal-dusted crust to family environments, Windsor Style Pizza has remained constant in Windsor, Essex County. But has Windsor Pizza been able to resist big Chains like Domino's or Little Caesars, and how does Windsor Pizza compare to the signature offerings in other notable “pizza cities”?
            </p>

            <a href="#section10" class="cta-button">Begin Exploring</a>
                  <div class="scroll-spacer"></div>
<div class="header-line"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>

